T1  - Dialectical Inquiry in Strategic Planning: Extending the Boundaries
AU  - Chanin, Michael N.
AU  - Shapiro, Harris J.
Y1  - 1985/10/01
PY  - 1985
DA  - 1985/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1985.4279092
